Ezekiel 20-25 <f>ⓙ</f> Moreover, I gave them statutes that were not good and rules by which they could not have life,
Ezekiel 20-26 and I defiled them through <f>ⓚ</f>their very gifts <f>ⓛ</f>in their offering up all their firstborn, that I might devastate them. I did it <f>ⓜ</f>that they might know that I am the LORD.
